INSERT INTO `submission_fields` VALUES (1,1,45,'Description_1','moonshot-the-indigenous-comics-collection-volume-2','text'),(2,1,47,'Description_2','moonshot-the-indigenous-comics-collection-volume-2','text'),(3,1,44,'Upload_Media_File_1','83cd0754c00ce53da20cf35f554eb42a_original.jpg','file'),(4,1,46,'Upload_Media_File_2','1c2b3e7399274c4ff00507bd9fcd119c_original.jpg','file'),(5,1,53,'LinkedIn_URL','https://www.LinkedIn.com/','url'),(6,1,54,'Twitter_URL','https://www.Twitter.com/','url'),(7,1,55,'MySpace_URL','https://www.MySpace.com/','url'),(8,1,56,'Home_page_URL','https://www.Homepage.com/','url'),(9,1,57,'Facebook_URL','https://www.facebook.com/','url'),(10,1,59,'IMDb_URL','https://www.IMDb.com/','url'),(11,2,45,'Description_1','Cat Cogliandro & catastrophe! present: The Story of Stories','text'),(12,2,47,'Description_2','Cat Cogliandro & catastrophe! present: The Story of Stories','text'),(13,2,44,'Upload_Media_File_1','acb0991ced3ed58fecff586acea4e5e0_original.jpg','file'),(14,2,46,'Upload_Media_File_2','907cda6f774763df250488b506a12cc2_original.jpg','file'),(15,3,45,'Description_1','1: An innovative quick release mechanism.  Current tripod mounts on the market today fall into one of two categories: screw, or spring. Screw mounts work like a vise; they allow for a secure grip, but are slow and cumbersome to operate every time you want to take your phone in and out of it. Conversely, spring mounts are quick to load and unload, but they have a flimsy grip and are not secure at all. We wanted to create a mount that is the best of both.  The solution we came up with took several rounds of iteration and engineering. The quick release lever, when opened, allows the jaws to move freely, making it easy to quickly load or remove your device. Here is the clever bit: when you close the lever, it automatically tightens around your device, resulting in a super secure connection. It\'s quick, and secure.','text'),(16,3,47,'Description_2','2: Portrait and Landscape   Very few tripod mounts on the market today can support a device in both portrait and landscape orientations. With things like panoramic photos, Periscope streams, and Snapchat, smartphones have legitimized the once-smirked-at portrait orientation. The Glif has a side mounted tripod mount, which allows devices to be mounted directly in portrait orientation. ','text'),(17,3,49,'Description_3','3: Extendability  We want you to consider the Glif as the starting point, the base, of your mobile photography rig. We want it to be a flexible tool that caters to your needs. As such, the Glif has a total of 3 tripod mounts, one on the bottom, one on the side, and one on the top. These allow you to add additional accessories, like a microphone or light.','text'),(18,3,51,'Description_4','What Devices Can the Glif Hold?  The Glif can hold devices roughly in width from 58 mm to 99 mm. This is essentially the range of a naked iPhone SE to an iPhone 6 Plus with a really thick case on it. In all likelihood, your device will fit. ','text'),(19,3,44,'Upload_Media_File_1','Iphone clip.jpg','file'),(20,3,46,'Upload_Media_File_2','Iphone clip2.jpg','file'),(21,3,48,'Upload_Media_File_3','Iphon clip3.jpg','file'),(22,3,50,'Upload_Media_File_4','Iphone4.jpg','file'),(23,2,53,'LinkedIn_URL','https://www.LinkedIn.com/','url'),(24,2,54,'Twitter_URL','https://www.Twitter.com/','url'),(25,2,55,'MySpace_URL','https://www.MySpace.com/','url'),(26,2,56,'Home_page_URL','https://www.Homepage.com/','url'),(27,2,57,'Facebook_URL','https://www.facebook.com/','url'),(28,2,59,'IMDb_URL','https://www.IMDb.com/','url'),(29,3,53,'LinkedIn_URL','https://www.linkedin.com/uas/login','url'),(30,3,54,'Twitter_URL','https://twitter.com/?lang=en','url'),(31,3,55,'MySpace_URL','http://www.facebook.com','url'),(32,3,56,'Home_page_URL','http://www.facebook.com','url'),(33,3,57,'Facebook_URL','http://www.facebook.com','url'),(34,3,59,'IMDb_URL','http://www.imdb.com','url'),(35,4,54,'Twitter_URL','https://twitter.com/','url'),(36,5,45,'Description_1','What Inspired The Codex?  The problem with puzzles today is they are either simple and cheap or hand crafted and supremely expensive. Yet once you\'ve solved either type of puzzle, you know the solution and have no desire to ever play with the puzzle again. The Codex addresses this issue of replayability by offering five puzzles in one, an intriguing story that ties everything together and a hidden storage compartment. On top of that, the beautiful design makes it perfect for putting on display in your home!','text'),(37,5,47,'Description_2','So Tell Us About The Puzzles Themselves! The first page is known as the Mechanical Iris, the portal that pulls in the apprentice after he attempts to open the puzzle book. Can you figure what is preventing the Iris from opening too?','text'),(38,5,44,'Upload_Media_File_1','Code 1.png','file'),(39,5,46,'Upload_Media_File_2','Code2.png','file'),(40,5,49,'Description_3','On the second page the user will encounter the Rotating Maze. A central dais and a peg must be used in a unique, dual-like motion in order to traverse the maze; however the catch is that the dais also hides the maze from the user’s view. How can you navigate a maze when you can’t even see where you are going?','text'),(41,5,51,'Description_4','The third page is called Geneva Gears, featuring a Geneva Wheel Mechanism and a series of gears hidden beneath a floor with various channels running throughout it. There are also six wheels which are also attached to gears of their own. The puzzler must place the gears in their respective places in order to unlock the page, but there are more slots than gears, so where do they fit? (Side Note: The final version of this page may feature changes to the design layout)','text'),(42,5,48,'Upload_Media_File_3','Code3.png','file'),(43,5,50,'Upload_Media_File_4','Code4.png','file'),(44,6,168,'LinkedIn_URL','http://www.LinkedIn.com','url'),(45,6,169,'Twitter_URL','http://www.Twitter.com','url'),(46,6,170,'MySpace_URL','http://www.MySpace.com','url'),(47,6,173,'IMDb_URL','http://www.IMDb.com','url'),(48,5,53,'LinkedIn_URL','https://www.linkedin.com/uas/login','url'),(49,5,54,'Twitter_URL','https://www.linkedin.com/uas/login','url'),(50,5,57,'Facebook_URL','http://www.facebook.com','url'),(51,5,59,'IMDb_URL','https://www.google.co.in/?gws_rd=ssl#q=imdb','url'),(52,6,171,'Home_page_URL','http://www.Home.com','url'),(53,6,172,'Facebook_URL','http://www.Facebook.com','url'),(54,7,160,'Upload_Media_File_1','download.jpg','file'),(55,7,168,'LinkedIn_URL','https://www.LinkedIn.com/','url'),(56,7,169,'Twitter_URL','https://www.Twitter.com/','url'),(57,7,170,'MySpace_URL','https://www.MySpace.com/','url'),(58,7,171,'Home_page_URL','https://www.Homepage.com/','url'),(59,7,172,'Facebook_URL','https://www.facebook.com/','url'),(60,7,173,'IMDb_URL','https://www.IMDb.com/','url'),(61,8,45,'Description_1','Why Oakland?  In the heart of Oakland\'s Fruitvale neighborhood, we will provide a feeling of home for the many of us for whom home can be an elusive thing. We\'ve lived in Oakland for over a decade and worked for social and economic justice in the face of gentrification, displacement, poverty, and violence against communities of color. Our vision for Reem\'s is to be like all loved Arab street corner bakeries - an anchor of the community creating good jobs for those who face barriers to employment, and providing delicious, nourishing food. ','text'),(62,8,47,'Description_2','We have an opportunity to secure a beautiful space in the Fruitvale neighborhood that will become a resource for fresh-baked daily bread, meals, and community gathering. The Fruitvale is one of the most ethnically diverse neighborhoods of Oakland, and we see Reem\'s offering a welcoming feeling of home across the many communities who live here.','text'),(63,8,49,'Description_3','Reem’s is one of three finalists in the nation-wide OpenTable Competition for aspiring restaurant owners. If we raise the most money, we\'ll win the grand prize worth over $38,000, including $15,000 in cash and coveted kitchen equipment from OpenTable. Your contributions will help us win the contest!   We are currently busting at the seams, working out of a commercial kitchen, producing hundreds of pounds of dough each week, and lugging equipment all over the Bay to bring the Reem\'s experience to customers in different locations. The number one question we get is \"Where can we find you regularly Do you have a storefront?\" Our dream is to say \"Yes! Come to Reem\'s every day!\"  Our goal is to raise as much money as we can toward our total funding goal of $300,000, which will permit us to do the full kitchen build out, buy equipment, furnish our space, and double Reem\'s team.','text'),(64,8,51,'Description_4','Six years ago, the dream of Reem\'s was born at the doorstep of a street corner bakery in Beirut, Lebanon. The scent of za\'atar, yeasted bread, and sweet orange blossom syrup right out of the oven and the sounds of laughter and chatter in Arabic all around me conjured up every forgotten memory I ever had of loving my childhood and every hope I\'ve ever had of creating home and community in the United States.    It was in watching the bread flying out of the oven, literally into hungry people\'s hands, and witnessing the life inside those bakery doors despite the political turbulence outside of them that I realized my people are masters of bread and hospitality: the lifeline of our history and what has kept us resilient over many generations despite colonization, war, drought, and famine in the Arab world. ','text'),(65,8,44,'Upload_Media_File_1','food1.jpg','file'),(66,8,46,'Upload_Media_File_2','food2.jpg','file'),(67,8,48,'Upload_Media_File_3','Food3.jpg','file'),(68,8,50,'Upload_Media_File_4','Food 4.jpg','file'),(69,8,53,'LinkedIn_URL','https://www.linkedin.com/uas/login','url'),(70,8,54,'Twitter_URL','https://twitter.com/login?lang=en','url'),(71,8,59,'IMDb_URL','http://www.imdb.com','url'),(72,9,161,'Description_1','Bolt M-1 : The Ultimate Urban Transporter','text'),(73,9,163,'Description_2','Bolt M-1 : The Ultimate Urban Transporter','text'),(74,9,160,'Upload_Media_File_1','bwfvddwvl0ff76bxpzc0.png','file'),(75,9,162,'Upload_Media_File_2','i5vobtcx1xitnouvzx7p.jpg','file'),(76,9,168,'LinkedIn_URL','https://www.LinkedIn.com/','url'),(77,9,169,'Twitter_URL','https://www.Twitter.com/','url'),(78,9,170,'MySpace_URL','https://www.MySpace.com/','url'),(79,9,171,'Home_page_URL','https://www.Homepage.com/','url'),(80,9,172,'Facebook_URL','https://www.facebook.com/','url'),(81,9,173,'IMDb_URL','https://www.IMDb.com/','url'),(82,10,71,'Upload_Media_File_1','13354971_1469923929.1004.jpg','file'),(83,11,45,'Description_1','Amica is unusual because his flock is a human family in the suburbs of Portland, Oregon. ','text'),(84,11,47,'Description_2','By day he roams the backyard, exploring, running, and building nests, along with his friends the chickens and the dog.','text'),(85,11,49,'Description_3','At night, he sleeps in the living room with his friend the cat. He loves to watch television with the family—British shows are his favorites.','text'),(86,11,51,'Description_4','Rheas are native to South America, where they are hunted as game; in the US and Europe they are primarily raised as livestock. In Amica\'s World, you\'ll see that they are highly intelligent and expressive animals, with a range of emotions similar to humans.','text'),(87,11,44,'Upload_Media_File_1','Publish2.jpg','file'),(88,11,46,'Upload_Media_File_2','Publish3.jpg','file'),(89,11,48,'Upload_Media_File_3','Publish4.jpg','file'),(90,11,50,'Upload_Media_File_4','Publish5.jpg','file'),(91,10,96,'LinkedIn_URL','http://www.Facebook.com','url'),(92,10,97,'Twitter_URL','http://www.Twitter.com','url'),(93,10,98,'MySpace_URL','http://www.MySpace.com','url'),(94,10,99,'Home_page_URL','http://www.Home.com','url'),(95,10,100,'Facebook_URL','http://www.Facebook.com','url'),(96,10,102,'IMDb_URL