 engrave it on your pen for an added personal touch.  Important: The wood grain has a lot of detail, so small detailed signatures might be hard to see especially on the smaller barreled pens.  ','text'),(114,14,49,'Description_3','To add an Add-on to you pledge follow these instructions:   1) Press the \"manage your pledge\" button above. If you have not yet pledged it will say \"back this project\"  2) Increase your pledge in the \"Pledge Amount\" box by the total of the add-ons you want to add.    3) After the end of the Kickstarter campaign you will receive a survey that will ask you questions so that you can explain how you would like the add-on money assigned.    All items will ship in a velvet pouch or sleeve. ','text'),(115,14,51,'Description_4','The cufflinks are approximately 3/4\" square and come with chrome hardware.','text'),(116,14,44,'Upload_Media_File_1','pen2.jpg','file'),(117,14,46,'Upload_Media_File_2','pen3.jpg','file'),(118,14,48,'Upload_Media_File_3','pen4.jpg','file'),(119,14,50,'Upload_Media_File_4','pen5.jpg','file'),(120,14,53,'LinkedIn_URL','https://www.linkedin.com/uas/login','url'),(121,14,54,'Twitter_URL','https://twitter.com/login?lang=en','url'),(122,14,57,'Facebook_URL','https://www.facebook.com','url'),(123,14,59,'IMDb_URL','http://www.imdb.com','url'),(124,15,71,'Upload_Media_File_1','13377767_1470017476.1457.jpg','file'),(125,15,96,'LinkedIn_URL','https://www.LinkedIn.com/','url'),(126,15,97,'Twitter_URL','https://www.Twitter.com/','url'),(127,15,98,'MySpace_URL','https://www.MySpace.com/','url'),(128,15,99,'Home_page_URL','https://www.Homepage.com/','url'),(129,15,100,'Facebook_URL','https://www.facebook.com/','url'),(130,15,102,'IMDb_URL','https://www.IMDb.com/','url'),(131,16,71,'Upload_Media_File_1','13376997_1470013465.8921.jpg','file'),(132,16,96,'LinkedIn_URL','https://www.LinkedIn.com/','url'),(133,16,97,'Twitter_URL','https://www.Twitter.com/','url'),(134,16,98,'MySpace_URL','https://www.MySpace.com/','url'),(135,16,99,'Ho