In_URL','https://www.LinkedIn.com/','url'),(161,19,97,'Twitter_URL','https://www.Twitter.com/','url'),(162,19,98,'MySpace_URL','https://www.MySpace.com/','url'),(163,19,99,'Home_page_URL','https://www.Homepage.com/','url'),(164,19,100,'Facebook_URL','https://www.facebook.com/','url'),(165,19,102,'IMDb_URL','https://www.IMDb.com/','url'),(166,20,45,'Description_1','Let\'s make one thing abundantly clear: these ain\'t just camera bags. They\'re Everyday bags—crafted by a team of designers, engineers, and photographers to meet the needs of everyone in the modern world.','text'),(167,20,47,'Description_2','We may have cut our teeth in the camera accessories world, but these bags are for everyone, just like our (award-winning*) Everyday Messenger that we designed and launched a year ago with the help of renowned adventure photographer Trey Ratcliff.','text'),(168,20,49,'Description_3','Simply put, a backpack without compromises. Available in Charcoal and Ash, and in 20L and 30L sizes. Unless otherwise specified, all pictures are of the 20L Everyday Backpack.','text'),(169,20,44,'Upload_Media_File_1','bag23.png','file'),(170,20,46,'Upload_Media_File_2','bag3.png','file'),(171,20,48,'Upload_Media_File_3','bag4.png','file'),(172,20,53,'LinkedIn_URL','https://www.linkedin.com/uas/login','url'),(173,20,54,'Twitter_URL','https://twitter.com/login?lang=en','url'),(174,20,57,'Facebook_URL','https://www.facebook.com','url'),(175,20,59,'IMDb_URL','http://www.imdb.com','url'),(176,21,71,'Upload_Media_File_1','13432785_1470190180.2587_funddescription.jpg','file'),(177,22,128,'Description_1','Hachina bibi','text'),(178,22,127,'Upload_Media_File_1','Hachina20Bibi20ENt20new_1469714433.jpg','file'),(179,22,135,'LinkedIn_URL','https://www.LinkedIn.com/','url'),(180,22,136,'Twitter_URL','https://www.Twitter.com/','url'),(181,22,137,'MySpace_URL','https://www.MySpace.com/','url'),(182,22,138,'Home_page_URL','https://www.Homepage.com/','url'),(183,22,139,'Facebook_URL','https://www.facebook.com/','url'),(184,22,140,'IMDb_URL','https://www.IMDb.com/','url'),(185,23,127,'Upload_Media_File_1','Beauti20Begam215_1470139001.jpg','file'),(186,23,135,'LinkedIn_URL','https://www.LinkedIn.com/','url'),(187,23,136,'Twitter_URL','https://www.Twitter.com/','url'),(188,23,137,'MySpace_URL','https://www.MySpace.com/','url'),(189,23,138,'Home_page_URL','https://www.Homepage.com/','url'),(190,23,139,'Facebook_URL','https://www.facebook.com/','url'),(191,23,140,'IMDb_URL','https://www.IMDb.com/','url'),(192,24,45,'Description_1',' Although they are the perfect size to clip in your pocket discreetly these folding knives are made to be seen. With a balanced design and visual appeal the comfort of the knives was not overlooked.','text'),(193,24,47,'Description_2','An everyday carry tool needs to be able to withstand your everyday grind, so we’ve built these knives out of some tough materials.','text'),(194,24,49,'Description_3','The body is made of Grade 5 Titanium, a metal known for its strength and minimal weight. The blade is made of hardened D2 Steel, known for its sharpness and toughness.  Every component is made with the tightest tolerances, resulting in a strong, sturdy, and lightweight knife that is made to do work. Not to mention the look and feel of these knives are fantastic.','text'),(195,24,51,'Description_4','1) The Strand is a frame lock design with a blade that is 2.8 inches, housed in a sturdy titanium frame. A great everyday carry and camping knife. Weight is 3.2 oz.','text'),(196,24,44,'Upload_Media_File_1','titan2.jpg','file'),(197,24,46,'Upload_Media_File_2','titan3.jpg','file'),(198,24,48,'Upload_Media_File_3','titan4.jpg','file'),(199,24,50,'Upload_Media_File_4','titan5.jpg','file'),(200,24,53,'LinkedIn_URL','https://www.linkedin.com/uas/login','url'),(201,24,54,'Twitter_URL','https://twitter.com/login?lang=en','url'),(202,24,57,'Facebook_URL','https://www.facebook.com','url'),(203,24,59,'IMDb_URL','http://www.imdb.com','url'),(204,25,128,'Description_1','Samiran Das','text'),(205,25,127,'Upload_Media_File_1','Drapadi20Das_1470143466.jpg','file'),(206,25,135,'LinkedIn_URL','https://www.LinkedIn.com/','url'),(207,25,136,'Twitter_URL','https://www.Twitter.com/','url'),(208,25,137,'MySpace_URL','https://www.MySpace.com/','url'),(209,25,138,'Home_page_URL','https://www.Homepage.com/','url'),(210,25,139,'Facebook_URL','https://www.facebook.com/','url'),(211,25,140,'IMDb_URL','https://www.IMDb.com/','url'),(212,26,127,'Upload_Media_File_1','IMG-20160310-WA0005_1467027754.jpg','file'),(213,26,135,'LinkedIn_URL','https://www.LinkedIn.com/','url'),(214,26,136,'Twitter_URL','https://www.Twitter.com/','url'),(215,26,137,'MySpace_URL','https://www.MySpace.com/','url'),(216,26,138,'Home_page_URL','https://www.Homepage.com/','url'),(217,26,139,'Facebook_URL','https://www.facebook.com/','url'),(218,26,140,'IMDb_URL','https://www.IMDb.com/','url'),(219,27,45,'Description_1','After a couple weeks of discussion and design refinement, we modeled the first prototype in 3D. As you can see from the picture below, the design had taken on some smoother curves and aesthetically pleasing lines','text'),(220,27,47,'Description_2',' Now that we\'ve established how the project came about, lets talk about some of its great features. The CashStash is precision CNC machined from 6061-T6 aluminum which makes it light weight and comfortable on the belt loop. Then later anodized as the standard finish to give it a tough protective coating. First we can start with the emergency money chamber. This chamber is precisely machined to fit a rolled up dollar bill in the denomination of your choosing. It\'s also water tight to keep your emergency money clean and dry. Lastly the name \"CashStash\" was directly derived from this feature.','text'),(221,27,49,'Description_3','The next feature are the driver bit chambers. As with the emergency money chamber, these are also machined precisely to fit a standard 1/4\" drive bit. The caps on these chambers feature a high strength neodymium magnet so that when the cap is removed the bits are held securely to it and are easily removed from the body. Also as with the emergency money chamber these chambers are water tight to keep the bits clean and dry. Any standard 1/4\" drive bit will fit i.e. Phillips, Flat, Torx, Allen, etc..','text'),(222,27,51,'Description_4','The top of the CashStash body has a precise hex machined directly into it to accept any 1/4\" drive bit. The placement of the driver hex was one of the major aspects we spent significant time on to make sure it was comfortable in the hand as well as easy to use. Similar to the driver bit caps the hex driver has a high strength neodymium magnet to hold the bit securely while in use.','text'),(223,27,44,'Upload_Media_File_1','stash2.jpeg','file'),(224,27,46,'Upload_Media_File_2','stash3.png','file'),(225,27,48,'Upload_Media_File_3','stash4.jpg','file'),(226,27,50,'Upload_Media_File_4','stash5.jpg','file'),(227,27,53,'LinkedIn_URL','https://www.linkedin.com/uas/login','url'),(228,27,54,'Twitter_URL','https://twitter.com/login?lang=en','url'),(229,27,57,'Facebook_URL','https://www.facebook.com','url'),(230,27,59,'IMDb_URL','http://www.imdb.com','url'),(231,28,45,'Description_1','The first cascading wallet that works with only the thumb','text'),(232,28,47,'Description_2','Press with your thumb on the cards and made a movement up and down until the cards appear in cascading.','text'),(233,28,49,'Description_3','If you\'re not a funny guy, you can use the traditional way. it also works well. Simply push upward from the bottom edges of your cards.','text'),(234,28,51,'Description_4','Raw materials suppliers are reliable and recognized. They are able to answer my demands as numerous as they are or will be. If I’m no longer able to ensure the production. I’ve already visited a small factory near Toulouse who is ready to help me.  The delivery date is estimated on November 2016. According to the popularity of this project, the dispatch might be delayed if there are lots of contributors. To conclude the delivery will be done by chronological order.','text'),(235,28,44,'Upload_Media_File_1','wallet1.jpg','file'),(236,28,46,'Upload_Media_File_2','wallet2.jpg','file'),(237,28,48,'Upload_Media_File_3','wallet3.jpg','file'),(238,28,50,'Upload_Media_File_4','wallet4.gif','file'),(239,28,53,'LinkedIn_URL','https://www.linkedin.com/uas/login','url'),(240,28,54,'Twitter_URL','https://twitter.com/login?lang=en','url'),(241,28,57,'Facebook_URL','https://www.facebook.com','url'),(242,28,59,'IMDb_URL','http://www.imdb.com','url'),(243,29,45,'Description_1','For the ones who understand and appreciate the art of watchmaking and design and seek an exclusive and innovative Swiss Automatic Watch with the highest degree of craftsmanship.   DWISS is an independent designer watch company that produces creative, unique, and affordable luxury timepieces since 2011 and unlike the mainstream brands with their extremely high margins, we have a mission to offer a state-of-the-art product for its valuable real price .','text'),(244,29,47,'Description_2','SWISS MADE automatic timepiece ETA 2824-2 SWISS movement Unique and innovative time reading Limited edition of 199 per model Customized rubber strap Engraved butterfly deployant clasp Sapphire Crystal with Double Anti Reflective Coating  Water resistance 10 ATM (100m / 333 ft) •	28.800 bph / 25 jewels / 42h power reserve','text'),(245,29,49,'Description_3','M2 is the third model of our collection, the most innovative watch we ever designed and only with your help we will be able to produce it. A bold and eccentric timepiece with beautiful brushed and polished finishing made in 316L stainless steel. Measuring 43mm diameter, it’s composed of 9 parts fixed trough 23 screws with an exclusive and protected design. It uses a mechanical automatic ETA 2824-2 Swiss Made movement with 28,800 beats per hour, 25 jewels, power reserve approximately 42 hours and water resistance up to 10 ATM (100 meters).  The pioneering and innovative way of reading the time makes this watch a must-have for any serious watch collector, but also for everyone that is original and sophisticated, social active, looks for uniqueness and wants to stand out from the crowd.','text'),(246,29,51,'Description_4','About our capabilities:  As an established watch designer with industry experience of more than 10 years we have partnered with producers in Switzerland whom we know and with whom we have established a reliable and dependable collaboration. They produce our watches under our supervision since 2011.  Like every campaign in kickstarter if we don\'t reach our goal no one will be charged.  About the product:  We are confident that we will meet our projected delivery dates. All backers will be updated during the stages of production and development, with direct emails and posts in the campaign.  Prior to this Kickstarter campaign, we produced the samples you can see in videos and pictures. We tested them exhaustively to meet the highest standards of quality, so we got a product ready to rock and roll. LET’S DO THIS.','text'),(247,29,44,'Upload_Media_File_1','Dwiss1.jpg','file'),(248,29,46,'Upload_Media_File_2','Dwiss2.jpg','file'),(249,29,48,'Upload_Media_File_3','Dwiss3.jpg','file'),(250,29,50,'Upload_Media_File_4','Dwiss4.jpg','file'),(251,29,53,'LinkedIn_URL','https://www.linkedin.com/uas/login','url'),(252,29,54,'Twitter_URL','https://twitter.com/login?lang=en','url'),(253,29,57,'Facebook_URL','https://www.facebook.com','url'),(254,29,59,'IMDb_URL','http://www.imdb.com','url'),(255,30,135,'LinkedIn_URL','https://www.LinkedIn.com/','url'),(256,30,136,'Twitter_URL','https://www.Twitter.com/','url'),(257,30,137,'MySpace_URL','https://www.MySpace.com/','url'),(258,30,138,'Home_page_URL','https://www.Homepage.com/','url'),(259,30,139,'Facebook_URL','https://www.facebook.com/','url'),(260,30,140,'IMDb_URL','https://www.IMDb.com/','url'),(261,31,128,'Description_