g anymore! ','text'),(302,36,49,'Description_3','With a specially-designed high-powered modular battery which is easy to install, all you need to do is plug it in/out, you won’t be annoyed by the connector and the plug any more. The battery of Falcon FPV is user-friendly of higher security.','text'),(303,36,51,'Description_4','The Falcon FPV300 comes ready to fly right out of the box, with assembled drone body including an FPV camera and video transmitter. All you need is to pick up a pair of FPV goggles online or at your local hobby shop and you\'re ready to go. Racing drone has never been so accessible.','text'),(304,36,44,'Upload_Media_File_1','Airejet1.jpg','file'),(305,36,46,'Upload_Media_File_2','Airejet2.jpg','file'),(306,36,48,'Upload_Media_File_3','Airejet3.png','file'),(307,36,50,'Upload_Media_File_4','Airejet4.gif','file'),(308,36,53,'LinkedIn_URL','https://www.linkedin.com/uas/login','url'),(309,36,54,'Twitter_URL','https://twitter.com/login','url'),(310,36,57,'Facebook_URL','https://www.facebook.com','url'),(311,36,59,'IMDb_URL','http://www.imdb.com','url'),(312,37,127,'Upload_Media_File_1','eyetreatment.jpg','file'),(313,37,135,'LinkedIn_URL','https://www.LinkedIn.com/','url'),(314,37,136,'Twitter_URL','https://www.Twitter.com/','url'),(315,37,137,'MySpace_URL','https://www.MySpace.com/','url'),(316,37,138,'Home_page_URL','https://www.Homepage.com/','url'),(317,37,139,'Facebook_URL','https://www.facebook.com/','url'),(318,37,140,'IMDb_URL','https://www.IMDb.com/','url'),(319,38,45,'Description_1','Karam Kitchen will start by offering group catering in the form of crowd-pleasing platter options. (Our smoky eggplant dip, called Mutabel, and our Lamb and Beef skewers are incredible!) See our sample menu here. We are proud members of The Kitchen Collective, which will be our home base for cooking. Joining The Collective means we already have a commercial licensed cooking available to us! Our three founding chefs are newly arrived Syrian refugees to Hamilton with amazing cooking skills. They are partnering with Brittani Farrington and Kim Kralt, who bring years of experience in restaurant management, catering, and quick service marketing. We hope to be able to hire more newcomers as soon as business growth allows!','text'),(320,38,47,'Description_2','We\'ve received incredible support from the Hamilton community and the Planning & Economic Development Department of City Hall. All we need now is funding to take us to market! In addition to fulfilling the perks on the right, we\'ll be using the money for:  Business Licensing  Kitchen Fees Insurance Ingredients for Menu Development Packaging Equipment Pots and pans, cutlery, and all the other things you need to prepare a meal Specialized equipment to keep our food hot or cold while we deliver Printed Promotional Materials - including menus! An Arabic translator for business meetings','text'),(321,38,49,'Description_3','With your help, we can create a company that helps these three entrepreneurs build a new life in Hamilton, and contributes to our vibrant community. We hope that you\'ll consider donating. We look forward to preparing food for you!','text'),(322,38,51,'Description_4','While we’ve already come a long way in our business planning, a unique challenge of this business is the language barrier between our chefs and the broader Hamilton community. Your support will allow us to hire a translator as-needed to ensure operations run smoothly.  Any new business faces the challenge of getting the word out. We hope that you’ll help us by ordering our amazing food, and inviting your friends to do likewise!','text'),(323,38,44,'Upload_Media_File_1','Food2.jpg','file'),(324,38,46,'Upload_Media_File_2','Food3.jpg','file'),(325,38,48,'Upload_Media_File_3','Food4.jpg','file'),(326,38,50,'Upload_Media_File_4','Food5.jpg','file'),(327,38,53,'LinkedIn_URL','https://www.linkedin.com/uas/login','url'),(328,38,54,'Twitter_URL','https://twitter.com/login','url'),(329,38,57,'Facebook_URL','https://www.facebook.com','url'),(330,38,59,'IMDb_URL','http://www.imdb.com','url'),(331,39,127,'Upload_Media_File_1','Bhagirathi.S.Gayakar1_1469674509.jpg','file'),(332,39,135,'LinkedIn_URL','https://www.LinkedIn.com/','url'),(333,39,136,'Twitter_URL','https://www.Twitter.com/','url'),(334,39,137,'MySpace_URL','https://www.MySpace.com/','url'),(335,39,138,'Home_page_URL','https://www.Homepage.com/','url'),(336,39,139,'Facebook_URL','https://www.facebook.com/','url'),(337,39,140,'IMDb_URL','https://www.IMDb.com/','url'),(338,40,45,'Description_1','I envision Junju as a lively and exciting bar and restaurant serving up modern and elegant plates using old-school Korean traditions like fermentation, live fire cooking, and spice.','text'),(339,40,47,'Description_2','Throughout the years, I\'ve cultivated strong relationships with some of the best farmers in the Bay Area who are doing amazing things, and together we are exploring heritage Korean seeds to really help push Junju forward.','text'),(340,40,49,'Description_3','The bar at Junju will draw inspiration from the street foods and drinking culture of Korea. Local architect IwamotoScott is designing the bar to capture the casual, lively spirit of Korean street stalls with an added touch of elegance. The bar will complement Junju’s late-night dining menu, which will add a much needed option for San Franciscans in search of post-midnight snacks. . We are working with some of the best bar minds in the area to curate a thoughtful, seasonal bar program.','text'),(341,40,44,'Upload_Media_File_1','Faod1.jpg','file'),(342,40,46,'Upload_Media_File_2','Faod2.jpg','file'),(343,40,48,'Upload_Media_File_3','Faod3.jpg','file'),(344,40,53,'LinkedIn_URL','https://www.linkedin.com/uas/login','url'),(345,40,54,'Twitter_URL','https://twitter.com/login','url'),(346,40,57,'Facebook_URL','https://www.facebook.com','url'),(347,40,59,'IMDb_URL','http://www.imdb.com','url'),(348,41,45,'Description_1','Wild Merman Salmon Jerky exclusively uses wild caught Alaskan Keta salmon, one of the most abundant and sustainable sources of protein on our planet.  Unlike other companies who use emulsified salmon, we only use whole muscle meat, which helps preserve salmon\'s delicate and valuable protein and omega-3 fatty acids. ','text'),(349,41,47,'Description_2','Each bag contains approximately half a pound of raw salmon and 24 grams protein. There are about 1.5 servings per bag, and 110 calories per serving.  We use wildflower honey to balance the savoriness of our jerky.  Our flavors are finely crafted, bold, and wild -- just like you!','text'),(350,41,49,'Description_3','Tracy O’Bryan is an animal lover, sustainability artivist (artist-activist), and master taste tester. A Chilean native, Tracy came to the US to study botany at the University of California Davis. She now lives with her fiance and Wild Merman co-founder Brendan Janet on a permaculture, community homestead in Tacoma, WA.','text'),(351,41,44,'Upload_Media_File_1','fish2.png','file'),(352,41,46,'Upload_Media_File_2','fish3.png','file'),(353,41,48,'Upload_Media_File_3','fish4.jpg','file'),(354,41,53,'LinkedIn_URL','https://www.linkedin.com/uas/login','url'),(355,41,54,'Twitter_URL','https://twitter.com/login','url'),(356,41,57,'Facebook_URL','https://www.facebook.com','url'),(357,41,59,'IMDb_URL','http://www.imdb.com','url'),(358,42,71,'Upload_Media_File_1','2d85c2ee-dfd6-4c5d-a2bc-f58134221124.jpg','file'),(359,42,96,'LinkedIn_URL','https://www.LinkedIn.com/','url'),(360,42,97,'Twitter_URL','https://www.Twitter.com/','url'),(361,42,98,'MySpace_URL','https://www.MySpace.com/','url'),(362,42,99,'Home_page_URL','https://www.Homepage.com/','url'),(363,42,100,'Facebook_URL','https://www.facebook.com/','url'),(364,42,102,'IMDb_URL','https://www.IMDb.com/','url'),(365,43,53,'LinkedIn_URL','https://www.linkedin.com/uas/login','url'),(366,43,54,'Twitter_URL','https://twitter.com/login','url'),(367,43,57,'Facebook_URL','https://www.facebook.com','url')